No. 09-11556. Jose Tolentino, Petitioner v. New York. 562 U.S. 1043, 131 S. Ct. 595, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 8865.

178 L. Ed. 2d 433,

November 15, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the Court of Appeals of New York granted.

Same case below, 14 N.Y.3d 382, 900 N.Y.S.2d 708, 926 N.E.2d 1212.
